title: 08/07 Fantasy Football Podcast: Cutler, Position Battles, Strategies
description:
Jay Cutler's signing is the top headline from the weekend, and today we discuss what it means for the Dolphins Fantasy assets (3:10). Any upgrades or downgrades? ... We've talked plenty about ADP, but now we want to know what you think. We read listener comments on current ADP (18:48). Are Martavis Bryant and Tom Brady being taken too early (22:30)? ... Some WR strategy talk (13:20), all the latest news including notes on Adrian Peterson (28:44), WAS RBs (30:30), OAK RBs (32:00) and Devin Funchess (33:04) ... Your emails at fantasyfootball@cbsi.com
